    "millsfield:images_texts": [
      "TWA\nTRANS\nWORLD\nAIRLINES",
      "• TWA-TRANS WORLD AIRLINES\nLockheed L-1049G Super G Constellation\nTWA operated twenty-eight Super G's on both domestic\nand international routes from 1955 to 1966. The first to be\ndelivered to the airline, named\n\"The United States,\"\nis\nshown over New York Harbor in 1955.\nPublished by Aviation World, Inc., P.O. Box 188, Bethel, Conn. 06801 U.S.A.\nL-021\n69800-0\npost card\nPhoto courtesy Trans World Airlines\nN7102C c/n 4583\n2002.113.456"
    ],
